sub_title: Student Artificial Intelligence at the University of Amsterdam
summary:
I am an ambitious student who likes to explore fun and interesting options. In my pastime I have tried a plethora of hobbies including: Python programming, art, poetry and livestreaming. Biology is also a field I am interested in besides AI and computers.

As an immigrant from China to the Netherlands, I had to study several languages to reach my goals. Whereas now I can speak Dutch, English and German. I am currently studying at the University of Amsterdam with a major in Artificial Intelligence. 

I am always open to new opportunities!
